{"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"sdbmhash"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Int","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si"},{"kind":"text","text":" { "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"get"},{"kind":"text","text":" }"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This algorithm was created for sdbm (a public-domain reimplementation of ndbm) database library."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"it was found to do well in scrambling bits, causing better distribution of the keys and fewer splits."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"it also happens to be a good general hashing function with good distribution."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the actual function is hash(i) = hash(i - 1) * 65599 + str[i];"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"what is included below is the faster version used in gawk."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"[there is even a faster, duff-device version] the magic prime constant 65599 (2^6 + 2^16 - 1)"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"was picked out of thin air while experimenting with many different constants."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"this is one of the algorithms used in berkeley db (see sleepycat) and elsewhere."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/swiftextras\/swift\/string\/sdbmhash"]}],"abstract":[{"text":"Hashed string","type":"text"}],"metadata":{"title":"sdbmhash","role":"symbol","modules":[{"relatedModules":["Swift"],"name":"SwiftExtras"}],"fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"sdbmhash","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Int","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"extendedModule":"Swift","symbolKind":"property","externalID":"s:SS11SwiftExtrasE8sdbmhashSivp","roleHeading":"Instance Property"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/SwiftExtras\/documentation\/SwiftExtras","doc:\/\/SwiftExtras\/documentation\/SwiftExtras\/Swift","doc:\/\/SwiftExtras\/documentation\/SwiftExtras\/Swift\/String"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/SwiftExtras\/documentation\/SwiftExtras\/Swift\/String\/sdbmhash","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"sections":[],"references":{"doc://SwiftExtras/documentation/SwiftExtras/Swift/String":{"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"String"}],"type":"topic","role":"symbol","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftExtras\/documentation\/SwiftExtras\/Swift\/String","kind":"symbol","title":"String","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"extension"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"String","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS"}],"url":"\/documentation\/swiftextras\/swift\/string"},"doc://SwiftExtras/documentation/SwiftExtras":{"url":"\/documentation\/swiftextras","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftExtras\/documentation\/SwiftExtras","abstract":[],"title":"SwiftExtras","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","role":"collection"},"doc://SwiftExtras/documentation/SwiftExtras/Swift":{"role":"collection","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftExtras\/documentation\/SwiftExtras\/Swift","abstract":[],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/swiftextras\/swift","kind":"symbol","title":"Swift"},"doc://SwiftExtras/documentation/SwiftExtras/Swift/String/sdbmhash":{"kind":"symbol","title":"sdbmhash","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/swiftextras\/swift\/string\/sdbmhash","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"sdbmhash","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Int","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"abstract":[{"typ